# Build context ignore rules for docker/Dockerfile.alpine ONLY.
#
# BuildKit automatically uses this file instead of the repo-root .dockerignore
# when the build targets this Dockerfile (`-f docker/Dockerfile.alpine`).
# It fully replaces the root .dockerignore (no merge).
#
# This image installs Matterbridge from npm and uses no source. The only files
# it copies from the context are ./.dockerbuild.json and
# docker/entrypoint.alpine.sh, so we ignore everything else.

# Ignore everything...
*

# ...except the two files this Dockerfile copies.
!.dockerbuild.json
!docker/entrypoint.alpine.sh
